 ## Validation Principle
 
 Use Git exit codes for applicability decisions. Show Git output to humans, but do not parse it for control flow.
+
+## Patch Metadata
+
+Patch-runner metadata may appear as leading comments before the first `diff --git` line.
+
+Repeated single-value fields are preferred over comma-separated lists.
+
+Example:
+
+```text
+# patch-runner: depends-on=000001
+# patch-runner: depends-on=000002
+```
+
+Dependencies are guardrails, not a package-manager solver.
+
+Patch IDs define intended order. A patch should not depend on a later patch ID.
